    "causal_summary": "After four HOLD verdicts (Phase 004 CPU-Qwen, Phase 005 CPU-ms-marco, Phase 007 MPS-Qwen, Phase 011/002 bge-v2-m3) plus an AI Council deliberation, the rerank arc reached the conclusion that no off-the-shelf or runtime-tuned reranker delivers a measurable quality lift for spec-memory's corpus. Phase 011/002 in particular returned **literally identical numbers to the OFF baseline** (hit-rate@5 0.12, NDCG@10 0.11, recall@5 0.12) at 19× the latency.",
